## 🔍 **Detection Commands**

### **Find Incorrect Flat-Percentage References**
```bash
# Find files with outdated coverage numbers
grep -rE "Integration.*(>50%|<20%|20%)" \
  --include="*.md" \
  --include="*_test.go" \
  --exclude-dir="archive" \
  . | grep -v "archive/"
```

### **Verify Correct ">=80%" Usage**
```bash
# Find files with correct per-tier coverage
grep -rE ">=80%" \
  --include="*.md" \
  --include="*_test.go" \
  .
```

